# 5. Machine Learning Model  
Algorithm: **RandomForestRegressor**

### ğŸ”¢ Performance Metrics  
| Metric | Value |
|--------|--------|
| MAE | 1.503 |
| RMSE | 1.885 |
| RÂ² | 0.916 |

### Interpretation  
- The model explains **91.6%** of the variance â†’ excellent  
- Low prediction error (â‰ˆ 1.5 points)  
- Most influential variables:  
  - study_hours  
  - reading_score  
  - writing_score  
  - test_preparation  

---

# 6. Conclusion  

This analysis shows:

- Students generally perform well
- Test preparation significantly increases performance
- Gender has little impact on performance
- Study hours have a strong but nonlinear influence
- Machine learning provides accurate score predictions

